eserved branch and salvage/cherry-pick commit `52ff82f8275e51f1362feb54cfd9fc8a6b4c5d3e` if the API adaptation looks correct.\n2. Rerun the metrics/publication portion of the workflow, or rerun the full workflow from the preserved branch, and verify it detects the changed test and metadata files instead of recording `test_file: None` / `metadata_file: None`.\n3. Check why the dynamic-access report for `4.0.0` is `0/0` despite the passing test run if coverage is required for this lane."}}
